=Description=

"The Zero State (ZS) community works toward the establishment of a VDPS (Virtual/Distributed/Parallel State) committed to Social Futurism and the WAVE Principles. ZS is affiliated with the Institute for Social Futurism (ISF) via the WAVE movement network.

ZS’ goal is the establishment of a trans-national, virtual state – the Zero State. It should be stressed that ZS does not advocate total abolition of the state. ZS works toward the establishment of an emphatically voluntarist, virtual state structure which has powers of governance strictly limited by jurisdiction."
(http://socialfuturism.net/affiliates/zero-state-zs/)

